Citation.sTitle: Solubilities of Sulfadiazine in Methanol, Ethanol, 1-Propanol, 2-Propanol, Acetone, and Chloroform from (294.15 to 318.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of sulfadiazine in methanol, ethanol, 1-propanol, 2-propanol, acetone, and chloroform have been determined with temperatures from (294.15 to 318.15) K by a static equilibrium method. The experimental data were correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
